{"tid":2122313,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《花木蘭》無得留低，正式從美上映檔期中剔除","createTime":"2020-07-24T02:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T04:01:23.000Z","uid":35562,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b1488ea255fb621cbe4468bf8e755a011e1151f5","tid":2122313,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:34:29.000Z","msg":"#自稱Asian非Chinese美籍出走內地藝人撐港警暴行演員劉亦菲 主演的Disney真人版《花木蘭》電影因武肺疫情在美國三度延期上映，今日官方確認將電影移出未來上映檔期計劃，未知會否轉到Disney+點播平台上播出及其它地區包括香港會否同樣撤出戲院上映計劃。<br />\n<br />\n《花木蘭》原定3月27日在美國公映更已舉行首映會，但在武肺大爆發下宣布延到7月24日，及後再度延期到8月21日，而今次則正式移出上映計劃。🎇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MeiKekNin/photos/a.589287414568604/1622226174608051/?type=3&amp;__tn__=H-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMeiKekNin%2Fphotos%2Fa.589287414568604%2F1622226174608051%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26__tn__%3DH-R&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=f7c82b19\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MeiKekNin/photos/a.589287414568604/1622226174608051/?type=3&amp;__tn__=H-R</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/disney-unschedules-mulan-pushes-back-avatar-star-wars-films-a-year-1304133?fbclid=IwAR0QBvNnSD6okN3zkW7EFoOsZZinxVrN4Dbh-Ic1ijwpUW0dtOJl9hEURVI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fnews%2Fdisney-unschedules-mulan-pushes-back-avatar-star-wars-films-a-year-1304133%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0QBvNnSD6okN3zkW7EFoOsZZinxVrN4Dbh-Ic1ijwpUW0dtOJl9hEURVI&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=0be39a81\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/disney-unschedules-mulan-pushes-back-avatar-star-wars-films-a-year-1304133?fbclid=IwAR0QBvNnSD6okN3zkW7EFoOsZZinxVrN4Dbh-Ic1ijwpUW0dtOJl9hEURVI</a>"},{"pid":"7f17522f26a85d37feec1927b7e9ca3782de6059","tid":2122313,"uid":238370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\